#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.33:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.33:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga "
msgstr "4. Deities "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Hirigāravasutta "
msgstr "33. Respect for Conscience "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.29, sc1
msgctxt "an7.33:1.1"
msgid "“Imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, sā devatā maṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, tonight, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, came to me, bowed, stood to one side, and said to me: "

msgctxt "an7.33:1.2"
msgid "‘sattime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "‘Sir, these seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

msgctxt "an7.33:1.3"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.33:1.4"
msgid "Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, samādhigāravatā, hirigāravatā, ottappagāravatā. "
msgstr "Respect for the Teacher, for the teaching, for the Saṅgha, for the training, for immersion, for conscience, and for prudence. "

msgctxt "an7.33:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhante, satta dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī’ti. "
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.33:1.6"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā. "
msgstr "That is what that deity said. "

msgctxt "an7.33:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then he bowed and respectfully circled me, keeping me on his right side, before vanishing right there. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.33:2.1"
msgid "Satthugaru dhammagaru, "
msgstr "Respect for the Teacher and the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe ca tibbagāravo; "
msgstr "and keen respect for the Saṅgha; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.3"
msgid "Samādhigaru ātāpī, "
msgstr "respect for immersion, being energetic, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.4"
msgid "sikkhāya tibbagāravo. "
msgstr "and keen respect for the training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.33:3.1"
msgid "Hiriottappasampanno, "
msgstr "One with both conscience and prudence, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.2"
msgid "sappatisso sagāravo; "
msgstr "reverential and respectful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.3"
msgid "Abhabbo parihānāya, "
msgstr "can’t decline, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.4"
msgid "nibbānasseva santike”ti. "
msgstr "and has drawn near to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.33:3.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
